<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 20:07:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>阿根廷米雷任命前新纳粹分子为国家最高法律办公室主任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/argentinas-melei-appoints-former-neo-nazi-as-head-of-national-top-legal-office/0000018c-3023-da74-afce-b5fb4d9d0000</link><description>就任阿根廷总统不到两周后，这位自称“以色列粉丝”的人选择鲁道夫·巴拉（Rodolfo Barra）领导财政部检察办公室，尽管他此前因加入暴力反犹太主义团体而被迫辞去政府职务</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 17:31:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/argentinas-melei-appoints-former-neo-nazi-as-head-of-national-top-legal-office/0000018c-3023-da74-afce-b5fb4d9d0000</guid></item><item><title>国际刑事法院检察官称哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列人为“严重国际罪行”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/icc-prosecutor-calls-oct-7-hamas-attack-on-israelis-serious-international-crimes/0000018c-3069-da74-afce-b5f926bb0000</link><description>卡里姆·汗呼吁释放被绑架到加沙的人质，称他们不应该被用作“人体盾牌或讨价还价的筹码”，并呼吁以色列将其军事反应限制在“明确的法律范围内”</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 17:15:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/icc-prosecutor-calls-oct-7-hamas-attack-on-israelis-serious-international-crimes/0000018c-3069-da74-afce-b5f926bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列拥有的船只在红海遭到导弹袭击；也门胡塞武装声称对此事负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/israeli-owned-ship-attacked-by-missiles-in-red-sea-yemens-houthis-claim-responsibility/0000018c-3077-dc03-a9ec-3c7f413f0000</link><description>也门胡塞武装发言人准将。叶海亚·萨里将军对袭击事件负责，称第一艘船在连接红海和亚丁湾的曼德海峡被导弹击中，第二艘船被无人机击中</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 16:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/israeli-owned-ship-attacked-by-missiles-in-red-sea-yemens-houthis-claim-responsibility/0000018c-3077-dc03-a9ec-3c7f413f0000</guid></item><item><title>自从10月7日失去亲人以来，这些以色列人专注于推翻内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/since-losing-their-loved-ones-on-oct-7-these-israelis-focus-on-ousting-netanyahu/0000018c-2ffe-dc03-a9ec-3fff17d60000</link><description>雅科夫·戈多（Ya&amp;#39;akov Godo）和马兹·伊农（Maoz Inon）在哈马斯的恶毒袭击中失去了挚爱的家人，他们在悲痛中团结在一起，不允许自己屈服于仇恨，并共同努力推动现任极右翼政府下台。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 16:26:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/since-losing-their-loved-ones-on-oct-7-these-israelis-focus-on-ousting-netanyahu/0000018c-2ffe-dc03-a9ec-3fff17d60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡不会下台。这些是驱逐他的其他方法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-wont-step-down-these-are-the-other-ways-to-oust-him/0000018c-2fe2-da74-afce-affb02c50000</link><description>政府叛变。不信任投票。公众抗议。这些都是推翻总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的权力的方法，以及在以色列与哈马斯战争仍在进行期间发生这些方法的可能性</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 16:08:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-wont-step-down-these-are-the-other-ways-to-oust-him/0000018c-2fe2-da74-afce-affb02c50000</guid></item><item><title>下一场中东大对决：内塔尼亚胡 vs 拜登</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/ever-ungrateful-beleaguered-netanyahu-looks-to-confront-biden-over-gaza/0000018c-2f6c-df3f-a58c-ff7ff2fb0000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以来，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡通常认为乔·拜登的政治慷慨是理所当然的。美国总统将不得不就战后加沙日益不相容的愿景与以色列总理对峙的时刻即将到来。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 15:07:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/ever-ungrateful-beleaguered-netanyahu-looks-to-confront-biden-over-gaza/0000018c-2f6c-df3f-a58c-ff7ff2fb0000</guid></item><item><title>伦敦议会在公众强烈反对后撤销了烛台安装的取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/london-council-reverses-cancellation-of-menorah-installation-following-public-backlash/0000018c-2ffd-dc03-a9ec-3fff97110000</link><description>尽管官员们因反犹太主义事件增加而存在“加剧紧张局势”的风险，决定取消光明节的安装计划，但他们现在决定继续安装永久性烛台</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 15:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/london-council-reverses-cancellation-of-menorah-installation-following-public-backlash/0000018c-2ffd-dc03-a9ec-3fff97110000</guid></item><item><title>“你开始思考，他们会先杀掉女孩们，还是先杀掉我，然后再杀掉她们？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/you-start-thinking-will-they-kill-the-girls-first-or-kill-me-first-and-then-the-girls/0000018c-2fa9-d15f-a7af-bfaf32a30000</link><description>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列家庭：一个特殊项目 ■ 在奥姆里·米兰 (Omri Miran) 从纳哈尔·奥兹基布兹 (Kibbutz Nahal Oz) 被绑架之前，他的妻子莉莎 (Lishay) 有足够的时间告诉他，“不要成为英雄。”现在她想知道她和她的两个小女儿是如何幸存下来的</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 14:48:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/you-start-thinking-will-they-kill-the-girls-first-or-kill-me-first-and-then-the-girls/0000018c-2fa9-d15f-a7af-bfaf32a30000</guid></item><item><title>制裁巴勒斯坦的正义学生，但不要让他们沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/sanction-students-for-justice-in-palestine-but-dont-silence-them/0000018c-2f73-da74-afce-affb6e850000</link><description>巴勒斯坦正义学生会（SJP）因其对哈马斯恐怖主义的道德上令人反感的支持而应受到明确和普遍的谴责，并在其成员骚扰其他学生时受到纪律处分。但禁止他们进入校园是错误的反应</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 13:37:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/sanction-students-for-justice-in-palestine-but-dont-silence-them/0000018c-2f73-da74-afce-affb6e850000</guid></item><item><title>研究显示，哈马斯致命袭击一个月后，三分之一的以色列人出现创伤后应激障碍症状</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/study-one-in-three-israelis-exhibits-ptsd-symptoms-a-month-after-hamas-deadly-attack/0000018c-2f74-dc03-a9ec-3f7f185a0000</link><description>结果显示，在被问及 10 月 7 日事件的暴露程度时，34% 的受访者描述了与创伤后应激障碍相符的症状</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 13:25:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/study-one-in-three-israelis-exhibits-ptsd-symptoms-a-month-after-hamas-deadly-attack/0000018c-2f74-dc03-a9ec-3f7f185a0000</guid></item><item><title>苏珊·萨兰登在亲巴勒斯坦言论引发反犹太主义骚动后道歉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/susan-sarandon-apologizes-after-pro-palestinian-speech-ignites-antisemitism-uproar/0000018c-2f25-df3f-a58c-ff7fad400000</link><description>萨兰登因反犹太主义言论被联合人才经纪公司开除两周后，她在 X 上发帖称她的措辞是一个“可怕的错误”</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 12:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/susan-sarandon-apologizes-after-pro-palestinian-speech-ignites-antisemitism-uproar/0000018c-2f25-df3f-a58c-ff7fad400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质漫长的回家路：他们应该如何对待？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-hostages-long-road-home-how-should-israel-treat-them/0000018c-214c-d21c-abae-77fca0b00000</link><description>对于赎罪日战争后返回的战俘来说，治疗是零星的，对一些人来说甚至是创伤性的。专家表示，已经吸取了教训，但也指出造成当前危机的“难以想象的忽视”，并将造成严重影响。以色列知道如何帮助人质回家吗？</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 11:55:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-hostages-long-road-home-how-should-israel-treat-them/0000018c-214c-d21c-abae-77fca0b00000</guid></item><item><title>被士兵意外杀害的以色列家人抨击内塔尼亚胡说“这就是生活”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-accidentally-killed-by-soldiers-blasts-netanyahus-reaction/0000018c-2f05-da74-afce-affd318e0000</link><description>视频显示，周五在耶路撒冷阻止恐怖分子的以色列武装平民将枪扔在地上，举起双手，恳求到达现场的士兵不要开枪。 两名士兵接受宪兵询问</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 11:20:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-accidentally-killed-by-soldiers-blasts-netanyahus-reaction/0000018c-2f05-da74-afce-affd318e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列提议的加沙缓冲区不会带来它所寻求的安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-proposed-buffer-zone-in-gaza-will-not-bring-the-security-it-seeks/0000018c-2ebc-da74-afce-affd4a4e0000</link><description>缓冲区并不是一个新现象，埃及和土耳其的例子表明，缓冲区并不能阻止民族主义愿望、占领，甚至恐怖主义威胁。加沙的“安全地带”只会带来更多的流离失所，并使以色列国防军成为新的激进组织的容易目标</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 09:39:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-proposed-buffer-zone-in-gaza-will-not-bring-the-security-it-seeks/0000018c-2ebc-da74-afce-affd4a4e0000</guid></item><item><title>班图语系如何在非洲传播</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2023-12-03/ty-article/how-the-bantu-family-of-languages-spread-through-africa/0000018c-20c6-d9ef-abcd-3ee7f51e0000</link><description>基因研究支持班图人起源于 6,000 年前的西非，并随着时间的推移进行连续迁徙，穿过雨林进入与他们所知道的截然不同的景观</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 09:01:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2023-12-03/ty-article/how-the-bantu-family-of-languages-spread-through-africa/0000018c-20c6-d9ef-abcd-3ee7f51e0000</guid></item><item><title>38岁男子在以色列北部被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/38-year-old-man-shot-and-killed-in-nazareth/0000018c-2e95-dc03-a9ec-3eff3f9f0000</link><description>据以色列警方称，这是上周拿撒勒发生的第二起涉及司机的致命枪击事件</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 07:48:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/38-year-old-man-shot-and-killed-in-nazareth/0000018c-2e95-dc03-a9ec-3eff3f9f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布两名在加沙地带遇难士兵的姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-names-of-two-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-strip/0000018c-2e4e-d5f2-a5cc-6e5ef3180000</link><description>陆军宣布 11 月战斗中受伤士兵死亡，20 岁中士周六晚被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 07:08:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-names-of-two-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-strip/0000018c-2e4e-d5f2-a5cc-6e5ef3180000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军扩大在加沙地带南部的攻势，命令汗尤尼斯居民撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article-live/heavy-rocket-barrage-fired-from-gaza-at-tel-aviv-central-israel/0000018c-2ce8-dc03-a9ec-3cfb65190000</link><description>几名以色列士兵在黎巴嫩边境附近的反坦克导弹袭击中受伤 ■ 以色列国防军一夜之间袭击了加沙 400 多个目标，其中包括南部城市汗尤尼斯 ■ 加沙卫生官员：自周五上午停战结束以来，已有 316 人死亡 ■ 美国官员表示，没有就有关问题进行正式谈判人质获释 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有超过 159 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙至少有 15,500 人死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 04:02:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article-live/heavy-rocket-barrage-fired-from-gaza-at-tel-aviv-central-israel/0000018c-2ce8-dc03-a9ec-3cfb65190000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯需要延长停火，但拒绝付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/hamas-needed-to-prolong-the-cease-fire-but-refused-to-pay-the-price/0000018c-2c42-db3a-a1be-3ddf319d0000</link><description>在尝试与以色列谈判取得进展但失败后，哈马斯恢复了火箭发射 ■ 当以色列国防军为加沙长期战斗做准备时，拜登政府警告以色列的国际信用即将耗尽</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 03:56:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/hamas-needed-to-prolong-the-cease-fire-but-refused-to-pay-the-price/0000018c-2c42-db3a-a1be-3ddf319d0000</guid></item><item><title>两名巴勒斯坦人在西岸的不同事件中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-killed-in-separate-incidents-in-west-bank/0000018c-2c46-dc03-a9ec-3c7f2a760000</link><description>《国土报》获得的视频显示，定居者（其中一些人戴着面具）与以色列士兵一起站在约旦河西岸一个村庄被烧毁的房屋附近，几小时后在该村庄发现了一具男子的尸体。在另一起事件中，一名 14 岁巴勒斯坦人在纳布卢斯附近被士兵开枪打死，据士兵称，他拔出一把刀向他们走去</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 22:09:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-killed-in-separate-incidents-in-west-bank/0000018c-2c46-dc03-a9ec-3c7f2a760000</guid></item></channel></rss>